			<footer class="comment-meta">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
					<span class="fn">Seattle Sam</span> <span class="sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.aei-ideas.org/2014/04/creative-destruction-2013-newspaper-ad-revenue-continued-its-precipitous-free-fall-and-its-probably-not-over-yet/comment-page-1/#comment-423044"><time pubdate datetime="2014-04-26T10:58:25-04:00">April 26, 2014 at 10:58 am</time></a>
